<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you are a big bank and you want your employ=
ees to work from the office three days a week, and some of your employees d=
on=E2=80=99t do that, it seems pretty reasonable to send those employees a =
letter=C2=A0saying =E2=80=9Cour policies require you to be in the office at=
 least three days a week, you have not met that requirement, and if you kee=
p it up you might get fired.=E2=80=9D A lot of companies, understandably, h=
ave some sort of work-from-the-office policy, and if you have that policy, =
you will probably need an enforcement mechanism, warnings of consequences, =
records of warnings of consequences, etc., the whole apparatus of human res=
ources formality.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Still <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbu=
siness.com/click/34110962.258404/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvZTAyNz=
Q4ZWItZWY4MC00OTFlLWFiZDctNzgyMmZkYzg1Mzc0/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0aa8489=
0" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;"> the <em>language=C2=A0</em>here</a> just sounds like it was g=
enerated by an artificial intelligence set to =E2=80=9Cevil=E2=80=9D:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bank of America has sent =E2=80=9Cletters of e=
ducation=E2=80=9D to employees who have not been showing up at the office, =
warning them of disciplinary action, in the latest move from a large compan=
y to push staff back to the workplace.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One of the messages said its recipient had fai=
led to meet the bank=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9CWorkplace Excellence Guidelines=E2=
=80=9D for work location =E2=80=9Cdespite requests and reminders to do so=
=E2=80=9D.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CFailure to follow the workplace excel=
lence expectations applicable to your role within two weeks of the date of =
this notification may result in further disciplinary action,=E2=80=9D accor=
ding to the text of the letter that a BofA employee posted online.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You can say =E2=80=9Cshowing up at the office=
=E2=80=9D instead of =E2=80=9Cworkplace excellence expectations=E2=80=9D! T=
hat=E2=80=99s clearer and less, like, dystopian. You can call it a =E2=80=
=9Cwarning=E2=80=9D instead of a =E2=80=9Cletter of education.=E2=80=9D Why=
 does everyone have to be so=C2=A0<em>weird=C2=A0</em>about return-to-offic=
e.</p>
